data.description: Introducing a stunning Hill Country style home that will take your breath away! This charming one-story beauty boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Nestled on over 1 acre of land. Located in the prestigious gated community of Dancing Bear Ranch, this home provides exclusive access to the serene Medina Lake. Step inside and be captivated by the custom wood cabinets and the warm, inviting ambiance that permeates every corner of this home. The heart of this home lies in its big kitchen with a fabulous island, making it a dream come true for all the aspiring chefs out there! The spacious layout offers ample room for relaxation and entertainment, ensuring that every moment spent here is pure bliss. This property features a unique wood bridge leading to 400 sq ft of pet/animal fencing in the backyard, providing a safe and secure space for your furry friends to roam and play. But wait, there's more! The home also comes with an electricity-powered shed, perfect for storing all your outdoor equipment and tools. This gem comes with an incredible bonus - an additional 2-acre lot attached to it available for purchase, creating a sprawling oasis of over 3 acres!
